{
  "chapter": 99,
  "chapter_summary": "小鱼儿被困山腹，以自己为人质要挟邀月宫主释放铁萍姑。邀月宫主被迫照办，将铁萍姑抛入洞中。小鱼儿得逞后反而不肯出来，要挟邀月宫主去找花无缺赴约，并让其送来食物。苏樱推断出小鱼儿假死的两个逃生法子：一是等路过之人相救，二是利用长江潮汐退水找到出口。胡药师找到通长江的地道后急于逃走，却被苏樱揭穿小鱼儿并未真正下毒，只是吓唬他。苏樱劝说铁萍姑离开江玉郎，教她以冷淡报复负心人。小鱼儿坚持留在洞中等花无缺，声称自己掌握破解移花接玉的招式，苏樱等人担忧不已。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "说话人",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "想不到小鱼儿竞有这么大的本事，他死了后，竟连移花宫主都会为他伤心。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 2,
      "line_end": 2
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是什么人敢在此胡言乱语？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "你连我的声音都听不出了么？你莫非已忘记了，我在大便时，你还在门口闻过我的臭气哩！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你就是小鱼儿？你没有死？你在哪里？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我就在你面前，你都瞧不见我么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你可是在这山腹中？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我就是出不来，所以才只好在这里等你来救我，我算准了你一定会救我的，是么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 22
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，我一定会将你救出来的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "但你若不立刻放了铁萍姑，我就情愿死在这里。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 26,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你敢？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我为什么不敢？我现在想活就活，想死就死，移花宫主就算有通天的本事，可也拿我没法子，是么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "现在，我和花无缺的约会已经到时候了，你总不愿意我就这样死了吧？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 34
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "好，我放了她，绝不伤她毫发就是！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "我死了以后，你再杀她我也没法子，但我活着的时候，总要瞧着她也舒舒服服地活着才能放心。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你究竟要怎样？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这山洞虽深，但下面都是水，无论谁跳下来，都绝不会摔死。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "妙极妙极，想不到不可一世的移花宫主，竟是个呆子，你现在已将她交给了我，我更用不着听你的话了，是么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "现在花无缺又不在这里，我就算出来了，又有什么用？你见到我就生气，我瞧见你也不舒服，倒不如在这里还落得个眼不见为净。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但三月之期已经到了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不错，约会的时候到了，所以你快去将花无缺找来吧，我在这里等你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你在这里等？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "这山洞就像是个大酒罐子，就是你掉下来，也休想逃得出去的，你还有什么不放心么？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "何况，就算你不放心也没法子，现在只有我才是当家的，我若不想出去，就算十个移花宫主，也没法子请我出去的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "移花宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "花无缺是不是也已到了这里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "text": "不错，他已到了这里，只不过这山上的老鼠洞很多，你一时片刻也未必找得着他，若是找的时候太久，我只怕就要被饿死了，所以，你最好还是先弄些东西给我吃，我的口味，你是知道的，是么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yao_yue_gong_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "邀月宫主",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "不错，我是知道的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我……我说我对他……对他很好，那只不过是故意气移花宫主的，其实我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你用不着再解释了，我又不是醋罐子，何况对小鱼儿好的人又不止你一个，你就算对他好也没关系。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你对我好，我对你也不错呀，若不是为了你，我现在多多少少也可以听出一些有关移花宫主的秘密了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "移花宫主又有什么秘密？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我想知道她和我们家究竟有什么仇恨，她既然将姓江的恨之入骨，为什么又偏偏不肯自己动手，而且还要扮成什么见鬼的'铜先生'，逼着要花无缺来杀我，她不但骗了我，而且对她自己的徒弟也鬼鬼祟祟的，到现在为止，花无缺只怕还不知道铜先生就是他的师父。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "这些事的确奇怪，而且简直毫无道理。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "这其中的道理，也许只有她们姐妹两人自己知道，但看来我只要活着，她们是绝不会说出来。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "也许你就是要移花宫主认为你已经死了，所以才故意让江玉郎将你推下来，也许你自己知道这洞里都是水，是跌不死的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我怎会知道洞里有水？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "那时太阳还末下山，也许正好有一线日光照进来，反映出下面的水光。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "就算是这样，但我总也该知道，这么深的洞，一掉下来就出不去了的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你自然有法子的，而且法子还不止一个。外面说话的声音，洞里既然听得很清楚，外面有什么人走过，你一定也知道的，那么，你又不是哑巴，为什么不能叫人救你？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但……但那时候他并不知道这山洞是可以传声的。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "你也许不知道，但他从小在山谷中长大的，对这件事自然知道得很清楚。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "如此说来，在下实在是孤陋寡闻得很了。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "但这法子却有个漏洞。这里山势荒僻，万一没有人走过，他岂非就要被困死在这里，万一走过的不是他的朋友，而且是他的仇人，他又怎敢呼救。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "是呀，万一没有人走过，万一走过的都是他仇人，那又怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "所以他还有第二个法子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "你莫忘了，这座山就在长江口，这山腹里的水，就是江水，江水有潮汐涨落，潮涨的时候，这里的水也跟着涨，潮落的时候，这里的水也跟着退了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不错，这道理在下本来也该想得出的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "江水既然能流到这里来，那么这地方必定就有个出口直通长江，只要等到潮水退下去的时候，就可以找到这出口……",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "我说的法子对不对呀？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "你以为你很聪明么？真正聪明的女人都知道，她无论和哪个男人说话时，懂得的事都该比那男人少一些，你的毛病就是懂的实在太多了，这么样的女人，大多数男人都不敢领教。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你却并不是大多数男人，像你这样的人，天下只有一个……何况，这些道理你也知道的，我懂得还是比你少一些。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "如此看来，我迟早总有一天要被这丫头迷上的。",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "移花宫主果然听话，已将咱们的晚饭送来了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "他实在累了，这几天来，他吃的苦实在不少。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "若是换了别人，吃了他这么多苦，受了他这么多打击，纵然不意志消沉，也一定会怨天尤人的。但是你看他，他竟像是一点也不放在心上。这样的男人，你又怎么能怪我喜欢他。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你认不认得铁心兰？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我知道她对小鱼儿很好，可是……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "可是她除了小鱼儿外，还能喜欢别人，但我除了小鱼儿外，却再也不会爱上任何人了，所以我绝不能让她将小鱼儿抢走，无论用什么法子，我也要……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在这里，就在这里，我找到了！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你要睡，出去后再好生睡，现在咱们已经可以走了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我为什么要走？你难道没有听见我要在这里等花无缺么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你……你真的要等他？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "当然是真的，这约会三个月以前就约好了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但……但他来了之后，移花宫主一定会逼着他跟你打架的。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "'打架'这两个字用得不妥，像咱们这样高手相争，应该说是比武才对。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你们并不是比武，你们是要拼命呀！",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但你……你现在还不是他的对手，因为我知道那'移花接玉'功力神奇，实在是天下第一……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "但你可知道，普天之下，只有我一个人知道破解'移花宫'武功的招式。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "你真的知道……你怎么会知道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "自然是有人教给我的，'移花宫'武功的秘密，天下再也没有别人知道得比他更清楚了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "移花宫主又怎么将破解她自己武功的招式教给你？她难道疯了么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "但就算你能破解'移花宫'的武功，你也绝不会杀了花无缺的，是么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我杀不杀他，和你又有什么关系？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "text": "当然有关系，你不杀他，他就要杀你，你留在这里，就是……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu_er",
      "speaker_name": "小鱼儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们谁高兴走，谁就走，反正我是在这里等定了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在……在下有些不……不对了。毒……毒性只怕已发作。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "是他下的毒么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "那毒药是什么味道？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "咸咸的，湿湿的，还有些……有些臭气。",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "他只不过是故意吓吓你的，那一定不是毒药，你方才觉得毒已发作，只怕你自己心里在作怪。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "speaker_name": "胡药师",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "不是毒药是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_hu_yao_shi",
      "text": "我也不知道是什么，说不定就是他脚上搓下来的泥丸子。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你也不想走么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你难道不想再见江玉郎？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 258
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "我……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "我知道你一定想再见到他，因为你就算不再会喜欢他，难道你还会不想报复么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_su_ying",
      "text": "可是我却不知道该如何报复。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你可知道你现在为什么会难受？那只因为你觉得他对不起你，他抛弃了你，你觉得他根本未将你放在心上，所以你的心才会碎，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你若想报复，就要让他难受，让他觉得是你抛弃了他，让他觉得你根本就未将他放在心上，到了那时，他就会像条狗似的来求你了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_ying",
      "speaker_name": "苏樱",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "现在你懂得我的意思了么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 99,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    }
